list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Add custom data structures for ArrayList, LinkedList, and HashSet with test cases
- Implemented CustomArrayList to demonstrate ArrayList properties and basic operations - Created CustomLinkedList to illustrate LinkedList differences and functionality - Added CustomHashSet to explore HashSet uniqueness and hashCode-based handling - Provided test cases in Main to validate behavior of each custom data structure

task.summary:
Implement basic Java OOP structure with Person and Student classes
- Added Person class with encapsulation and PersonInterface implementation - Created Student class extending Person to demonstrate inheritance and polymorphism - Added main class for testing functionality of Person and Student instances - Verified encapsulation by modifying properties through setters
